<br />Hey, this is not about me. I just think that excluding half the people that have the console is not a very "polite" (for the lack of a better word) thing for a developer to do. I know that sometimes it's hard to make both PAL and NTSC crowds happy, but as a game developer I think that's something everyone should aim for.
<br />
<br />If smkd feels that this is just something to use in emulators, well, then so be it, but that would be throwing the potential of an engine like this in the garbage if you ask me.

		

